**story**
once up on a time,in a forest,there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree,which was on the banks of a river.
in the same forest,there lived the crocodile and his wife.
one day ,the crocodile came to the banks of river and rested under the tree.the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits.
the crocodile cameback the next day for more fruits,as he loved them.
as the days passed by ,the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.
